  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And the servants of Amon conspired against him,.... Some of his domestic servants, and perhaps his courtiers, not on account of his idolatry, but for some ill usage of them: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and slew the king in his own house: which they had an opportunity to do, being his servants. ",
        "children": [
